9th July 2015 ITV4
19:00 to 20:00 Stage 6 Highlights

Stage 6 is a long, flat stage that takes in over 100km of beautiful coastal scenery. This could again be a good day for the sprinters, but with the strong winds that frequently batter the north coast things might change in an instant. Presented by Gary Imlach with analysis from Chris Boardman, commentary from Phil Liggett and Paul Sherwen with Ned Boulting reporting at the roadside.
